{
  "texts": [
    "Average conservative vote rate circuit courts using 5% hand-coded Songer Auburn data, plotted by year and separately by economics and non-economics cases.",
    "Error spikes give standard error of the mean.",
    "Data weighted to treat judge-years equally.",
    "This is a 5% random sample of Circuit cases, available until the year 2002.",
    "The sample is hand-labeled for vote valence: liberal, conservative or neutral/hard-to-code."
  ]
